> +/*
> + * Guest driven VM boot component update device
> + * For details and specification, please look at docs/specs/vmfwupdate.rst.
> + *
> + * Copyright (C) 2024 Red Hat, Inc.
> + *
> + * Authors: Ani Sinha <anisinha@redhat.com>
